    TSynCppSyn, TSynEiffelSyn, TSynFortranSyn, TSynGeneralSyn, TSynJavaSyn,
    TSynM3Syn, TSynPasSyn, TSynVBSyn, TSynCobolSyn, TSynCSSyn,
